# State management artifacts — TRACKED BY DEFAULT (see knowledge/operational-patterns/state-management/filesystem-patterns.md)
# notes/ is intentionally tracked: progress.md, TODO.md, lessons-learned.md, current-task.md,
# impl-plan-*.md, and audit artifacts are first-class deliverables that survive sessions and
# machines. Exclusions below are for transient, private, or retroactively-scrubbed content only.

# Ad-hoc exclusion patterns (draft markers)
notes/scratch-*.md
notes/draft-*.md
notes/personal-*.md

# Organized drafts subdirectory
notes/_drafts/

# Archive escape hatch (retroactive scrub for content already committed)
notes/_archive/

_archive